  "description": "Adds in a large catalogue of 100+ paintings to the game!",
  "body": "![Logo](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/285e6d569d1a476c6b198a6b8c1eb175571651ad.png)\nPortfolio is a small mod & datapack that adds a catalogue of new paintings to the game, all of which were made by the artist [<u>**Yapetto**</u>](https://bsky.app/profile/yptsh.bsky.social). These include paintings such as Morning on the Seine, Justice, & Underworld.\n\n### The different catalogues of Portfolio\n<details>\n<summary>Still Life Catalogue - 1.0</summary>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d2f8f2dbc290f509a929ee382f93b6185894bb1c.png\">\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Void Manor Catalogue - 1.1</summary>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a088b34631297e611524006dd859f600fb67e4ce.png\">\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Death Catalogue - 1.2</summary>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/eecdb51577c9fcf86767fe82e9b5d5349927b08b.png\">\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Rana Catalogue - 1.3</summary>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4af9c8dbb3a374a9018853f2285e7b844314ed6d.png\">\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>The Far Lands Catalogue - 1.3.5</summary>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/136c997b05135cad0e425556bd6d05bc8db81faa.png\">\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Anchor Catalogue - 1.4</summary>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/aae2bb2faf08324cbfdc23a6572b5e22aebbdd9f.png\">\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Giant Catalogue - 1.5</summary>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/800fb441ad894cc87953fcb35678859a72ae93f1.png\">\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Elemental Catalogue - 1.5</summary>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/61fa1b2f6ea7171c3a02bd16ff83affc4c3ae5a9.png\">\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Cloud Cuckoo Catalogue - 1.5.5</summary>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b03c9b68ed15bf04b645c12a887aaf74d42dc1db.png\">\n</details>",
